00\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000$\u0000\u0000\u0000org/apache/jackrabbit/webdav/client/PK\u0003\u0004\n\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000�y�;\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000,\u0000\u0000\u0000org/apache/jackrabbit/webdav/client/methods/PK\u0003\u0004\n\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000�y�;\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\"\u0000\u0000\u0000org/apache/jackrabbit/webdav/bind/PK\u0003\u0004\n\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000�y�;\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000$\u0000\u0000\u0000org/apache/jackrabbit/webdav/header/PK\u0003\u0004\n\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000�y�;\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000&\u0000\u0000\u0000org/apache/jackrabbit/webdav/property/PK\u0003\u0004\n\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000�y�;\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000)\u0000\u0000\u0000org/apache/jackrabbit/webdav/transaction/PK\u0003\u0004\n\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000�y�;\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\"\u0000\u0000\u0000org/apache/jackrabbit/webdav/lock/PK\u0003\u0004\n\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000�y�;\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\nURL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/apache/jackrabbit/2.0-beta4/jackrabbit-webdav/README.txt\n200 text/plain; charset=utf-8 3149\n====================================\nWelcome to Jackrabbit WebDAV Library\n====================================\n\nThis is the WebDAV Library component of the Apache Jackrabbit project.\nThis component provides interfaces and common utility classes used for\nbuilding a WebDAV server or client. The following RFC have been integrated:\n\n    * RFC 2518 (WebDAV - HTTP Extensions for Distributed Authoring)\n    * RFC 3253 (DeltaV - Versioning Extensions to WebDAV)\n    * RFC 3648 (Ordered Collections Protocol)\n    * RFC 3744 (Access Control Protocol)\n    * DAV Searching and Locating  (DASL)\n    * Binding Extensions to Web Distributed Authoring and Versioning (WebDAV) (experimental)\n\nIn addition this library defines (unspecified)\n\n    * Observation\n    * Bundling multiple request with extensions to locking\n\nCommon Questions\n================\n\nQ: Which WebDAV features are supported?\nA: DAV 1, 2, DeltaV, Ordering, Access Control, Search, Bind\n\nQ: This this WebDAV library provide a full dav server?\nA: T\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1782717985606}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_bXIhRgHoeIDBpS9obUq49qnF|fc_0dc0bb2d3206d7e8016a421e16e08081959f51bbe3da08ac44", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "[\n  {\n    \"latest\" : true,\n    \"metadata-version\" : \"1.5.0\",\n    \"source-code-url\" : \"https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/apache/jackrabbit/jackrabbit-webdav/$version$/jackrabbit-webdav-$version$-sources.jar\",\n    \"repository-url\" : \"https://github.com/apache/jackrabbit\",\n    \"test-code-url\" : \"https://github.com/apache/jackrabbit/tree/$version$/jackrabbit-webdav/src/test/java\",\n    \"documentation-url\" : \"https://github.com/apache/jackrabbit/blob/$version$/jackrabbit-webdav/README.txt\",\n    \"description\" : \"Jackrabbit WebDAV Library provides interfaces, utilities, and common classes for building WebDAV servers and clients. It supports core WebDAV functionality along with DeltaV versioning, ordered collections, access control, search, binding, observation, and related Jackrabbit WebDAV extensions.\",\n    \"tested-versions\" : [\n      \"1.5.0\",\n      \"1.5.2\",\n      \"1.5.5\",\n      \"1.6.0\",\n      \"1.6.1\",\n      \"1.6.2\",\n      \"1.6.4\",\n      \"1.6.5\",\n      \"2.0-beta1\",\n      \"2.0-beta3\"\n    ],\n    \"allowed-packages\" : [\n      \"org.apache.jackrabbit.webdav\",\n      \"org.apache.jackrabbit.commons.xml\"\n    ]\n  }\n]\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1782717985606}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_RcNwtTCDduQEfntxpGOux4mt|fc_0dc0bb2d3206d7e8016a4